window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>After gaining control of Pinnacle, life was easier, at least for a bit.</b></p> <p>We've located Psyche. My intel has led me to the other side of the world, where women glow and men plunder.</p> <p>Like the rest of the world, Australia has its own supe problems, a government cabal, and a mysterious secret in the center of that blasted land.</p> <p>I'm about to unravel them all.</p>"; 
